42:00.686 --> 42:03.177
Honey, you seen Sam? We're out of ice.

42:03.355 --> 42:04.595
I'll get it.

42:04.773 --> 42:07.435
I could use a break from all this anyhow.

42:08.110 --> 42:12.149
Well, thanks for having such a great time
at my party.

42:34.302 --> 42:36.042
Hello.

42:39.307 --> 42:41.639
That's not funny.

44:06.686 --> 44:09.473
Sookie, it's me. Sookie. Hey. Hey.

44:09.648 --> 44:11.730
He's in here. He almost--

44:11.900 --> 44:14.016
What, what?

44:17.906 --> 44:20.147
No,no,no,
please, please don't leave me.

44:20.325 --> 44:24.068
-Don't leave me. Please don't leave me.
-Okay, okay, okay, I won't.

44:24.246 --> 44:26.532
-I won't. I promise.
-Don't leave me.

44:46.226 --> 44:47.841
What the fuck?

44:59.906 --> 45:02.773
If you wanted to feed him,
we should've talked about it first.

45:02.951 --> 45:04.657
I don't need your fucking permission.

45:04.828 --> 45:08.116
Jason, if we don't trust each other,
how is he ever gonna trust us?

45:08.290 --> 45:10.622
This ain't a game,
I don't want him ending up dead.

45:10.792 --> 45:13.454
Oh, God, Jason, come on.
He's gonna kill us.

45:14.629 --> 45:15.664
No, he won't.

45:17.382 --> 45:19.964
I'm gonna let him go,
don't even try to fucking stop me.

45:20.135 --> 45:21.591
-Jason--
-No, please, don't.

45:21.803 --> 45:23.794
Get out of here! Goddamn.

45:23.972 --> 45:25.508
-Please, hurry.
-Yeah, I'm coming.

45:25.682 --> 45:27.138
-Please.
-I'm coming.

45:27.309 --> 45:28.970
People telling me what I can and can't--

45:35.233 --> 45:36.643
Fuck.

45:39.654 --> 45:41.645
If you want to torture anyone,
torture me.

45:41.823 --> 45:43.859
