45:51.207 --> 45:52.663
No.

45:53.835 --> 45:55.291
No, I was wrong to speak.

45:55.462 --> 45:57.123
You can quit stalling.

45:57.297 --> 46:00.460
What you see in this cow,
Mr. Compton...

46:00.634 --> 46:03.671
...is merely a response to stimuli.

46:03.845 --> 46:05.756
Humans are quite...

46:05.931 --> 46:07.796
...primitive...

46:07.974 --> 46:11.637
...incapable of feeling pain as we do.

46:11.811 --> 46:13.676
But you know that.

46:15.398 --> 46:17.059
Luisa.

46:21.488 --> 46:24.480
The Lord is my shepherd,
I shall not want....

46:24.658 --> 46:27.320
