46:27.494 --> 46:31.988
According to our records, you have
never been a Maker, is that right?

46:32.165 --> 46:33.405
Yes.

46:34.167 --> 46:35.668
But you know the procedure?

46:38.213 --> 46:39.874
Yes.

46:42.926 --> 46:45.042
Then proceed.

47:17.002 --> 47:18.742
Are you a Christian?

47:19.546 --> 47:21.662
I was.

47:22.757 --> 47:24.713
I'm a good girl.

47:25.885 --> 47:27.921
Jesus will take me home to heaven.

47:29.681 --> 47:30.761
What's your name?

47:31.891 --> 47:33.552
Jessica.

47:35.103 --> 47:37.264
Look at me, Jessica.

47:40.775 --> 47:42.766
You're safe now.

47:44.612 --> 47:46.648
Look in my eyes.

47:51.619 --> 47:53.780
Everything will be fine.

47:53.955 --> 47:55.365
I hate to interrupt...

47:55.540 --> 47:58.703
...but glamour is not permitted.

47:58.877 --> 48:01.038
-She's just a girl.
-You are boring me.

48:01.212 --> 48:03.464
Shut up and do as you're told.

48:10.263 --> 48:12.470
-It's all right. It's all right.
-No, let go.

48:12.640 --> 48:14.801
No, no. Let go of me! No!

48:14.976 --> 48:17.388
Stop it! Stop! No!

48:17.562 --> 48:19.098
No!

48:28.114 --> 48:30.230
-Forgive me.
-No.
